snippet.title: TETЯIS / PENTOMINOVICH - Trailer video
snippet.description:
Get it on google play! ►
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.elpatrixf.pentaminovich

A block stacking and line clearing game for android heavily inspired by TENGEN's version of the same game. Play it the way you want it, whenever you want it!

Also, get the PC version and the APK on gamejolt!
http://gamejolt.com/games/pentominovich/251460

--Quick before it's gone--
